A better way to handle sap custom code.

Updating your SAP systems means making a decision about how to handle your custom code. Is it better to use a manual approach, relying on developers, or automation and artificial intelligence, relying on technology? The answer, according to thousands of SAP customers, is smartShift.

Attention! Due to the jurisdiction of the European Court of Justice, the legal basis of data transfer regarding the use of our social media has changed. By clicking the "OK" button, you also agree to the data transfer to the USA. Details about your consent can be found on our privacy policy under "More".


